如果你的規則是：

驗證條件

1. 只驗證共有戶 (TS_CUST_ID 對應多個 SK_CUST_ID)
2. 只要該 TS_CUST_ID 底下有任何一筆 CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN (2,3)，整個 TS 跳過
3. 剩下的共有戶，比對：
    * 來源：所有 SK 客戶的最高風險等級
    * 目標：BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT.HIGHRISK
4. 差異筆數必須為 0

那完整驗證 SQL 可以寫成：

WITH JOINT_CUST AS
(
    SELECT TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    GROUP BY TS_CUST_ID
    HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
       AND MAX(
            CASE
                WHEN CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN (2,3)
                THEN 1
                ELSE 0
            END
       ) = 0
),
SRC AS
(
    SELECT
        s.TS_CUST_ID,
        MAX(
            CASE n.HIGHRISK
                WHEN 'H' THEN 3
                WHEN 'M' THEN 2
                WHEN 'L' THEN 1
                ELSE 0
            END
        ) AS SRC_RISK_NUM
    FROM JOINT_CUST j
    JOIN BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO s
        ON j.TS_CUST_ID = s.TS_CUST_ID
    JOIN Customer_Migrate_buffer c
        ON s.SK_CUST_ID = c.CustomerNo
    JOIN Cust_NP_Migrate_buffer n
        ON c.CIF_KEY = n.CIF_KEY
    GROUP BY s.TS_CUST_ID
),
TGT AS
(
    SELECT
        CustomerNo,
        CASE HIGHRISK
            WHEN 'H' THEN 3
            WHEN 'M' THEN 2
            WHEN 'L' THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS TGT_RISK_NUM
    FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
)
SELECT
    s.TS_CUST_ID,
    CASE s.SRC_RISK_NUM
        WHEN 3 THEN 'H'
        WHEN 2 THEN 'M'
        WHEN 1 THEN 'L'
    END AS SOURCE_RISK,
    CASE t.TGT_RISK_NUM
        WHEN 3 THEN 'H'
        WHEN 2 THEN 'M'
        WHEN 1 THEN 'L'
    END AS TARGET_RISK
FROM SRC s
JOIN TGT t
    ON s.TS_CUST_ID = t.CustomerNo
WHERE s.SRC_RISK_NUM <> t.TGT_RISK_NUM
ORDER BY s.TS_CUST_ID;

